  <entry>
    <title>difyTool模块解析</title>
    <link href="/2026/03/30/difyTool%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90/"/>
    <url>/2026/03/30/difyTool%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Dify-Tools-模块架构详解"><a href="#Dify-Tools-模块架构详解" class="headerlink" title="Dify Tools 模块架构详解"></a>Dify Tools 模块架构详解</h2><h2 id="概述"><a href="#概述" class="headerlink" title="概述"></a>概述</h2><p>Dify 的 Tools 模块采用<strong>三层流程架构</strong>设计，实现了从参数接收、工具决策到最终执行的完整生命周期管理。该架构通过职责分离，确保了工具调用的灵活性、可扩展性和可观测性。</p><hr><h2 id="第一层：组装与决策层（ToolManage）"><a href="#第一层：组装与决策层（ToolManage）" class="headerlink" title="第一层：组装与决策层（ToolManage）"></a>第一层：组装与决策层（ToolManage）</h2><h3 id="核心职责"><a href="#核心职责" class="headerlink" title="核心职责"></a>核心职责</h3><p>ToolManage 作为工具的<strong>入口调度器</strong>，负责接收外部参数、决策工具路由、组装完整工具实例。</p><h3 id="执行流程"><a href="#执行流程" class="headerlink" title="执行流程"></a>执行流程</h3><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="mermaid">sequenceDiagram    participant User as 外部调用者    participant TM as ToolManage    participant DB as 数据库/配置    participant RT as ToolRuntime        User->>TM: 调用 get_tool_runtime(provider, name)    TM->>TM: 确定 Provider 类型    TM->>DB: 查询凭证与配置信息    DB-->>TM: 返回加密凭证    TM->>TM: 解密凭证 (decrypted_credentials)        Note over TM, RT: 构建上下文实体    TM->>RT: 实例化 ToolRuntime    RT-->>TM: 返回 runtime 实例        TM->>TM: 执行 fork_tool_runtime    Note right of TM: 合并 Runtime + Tool 定义    TM-->>User: 返回完整工具实例 (Ready to Invoke)</pre></div></figure><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-python" data-language="python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">get_credentials_schema</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>self<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token operator">></span> <span class="token builtin">list</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span>ProviderConfig<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>        <span class="token triple-quoted-string string">"""        returns the credentials schema of the provider        :return: the credentials schema        """</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> deepcopy<span class="token punctuation">(</span>self<span class="token punctuation">.</span>entity<span class="token punctuation">.</span>credentials_schema<span class="token punctuation">)</span>    <span class="token decorator annotation punctuation">@abstractmethod</span>    <span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">get_tool</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>self<span class="token punctuation">,</span> tool_name<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token operator">></span> Tool<span class="token punctuation">:</span>        <span class="token triple-quoted-string string">"""        returns a tool that the provider can provide        :return: tool        """</span>        <span class="token keyword">pass</span>    <span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">validate_credentials_format</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>self<span class="token punctuation">,</span> credentials<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">dict</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> Any<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><p>这个provider的作用就是获得供应商的信息，同时返回tool实例，我们通过供应商返回的信息进行验证和前端渲染表单</p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-python" data-language="python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">from</span> typing <span class="token keyword">import</span> Any<span class="token keyword">from</span> pydantic <span class="token keyword">import</span> BaseModel<span class="token punctuation">,</span> Field<span class="token keyword">from</span> core<span class="token punctuation">.</span>app<span class="token punctuation">.</span>entities<span class="token punctuation">.</span>app_invoke_entities <span class="token keyword">import</span> InvokeFrom<span class="token keyword">from</span> core<span class="token punctuation">.</span>plugin<span class="token punctuation">.</span>entities<span class="token punctuation">.</span>plugin_daemon <span class="token keyword">import</span> CredentialType<span class="token keyword">from</span> core<span class="token punctuation">.</span>tools<span class="token punctuation">.</span>entities<span class="token punctuation">.</span>tool_entities <span class="token keyword">import</span> ToolInvokeFrom<span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">ToolRuntime</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>BaseModel<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>    <span class="token triple-quoted-string string">"""    Meta data of a tool call processing    """</span>    tenant_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span>  <span class="token comment"># 租户ID - 标识当前工作空间/组织，用于权限隔离和数据隔离</span>    tool_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token comment"># 工具标识 - 具体调用的工具ID</span>    invoke_from<span class="token punctuation">:</span> InvokeFrom <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token comment"># 调用来源 - 标识从何处触发（如 Debugger、WebApp、ServiceAPI 等）</span>    tool_invoke_from<span class="token punctuation">:</span> ToolInvokeFrom <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token comment"># 工具调用来源 - 区分是 Agent 调用、Workflow 调用还是直接调用</span>    credentials<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">dict</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> Any<span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> Field<span class="token punctuation">(</span>default_factory<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token builtin">dict</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token comment"># 凭证信息 - 存储 API Key、Token 等敏感认证信息</span>    credential_type<span class="token punctuation">:</span> CredentialType <span class="token operator">=</span> Field<span class="token punctuation">(</span>default<span class="token operator">=</span>CredentialType<span class="token punctuation">.</span>API_KEY<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token comment"># 凭证类型 - 如 API_KEY、OAUTH2 等</span>    runtime_parameters<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">dict</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> Any<span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> Field<span class="token punctuation">(</span>default_factory<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token builtin">dict</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token comment"># 运行时参数 - 动态传入的额外配置参数</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><p>runtime用来存储工具执行所需的所有上下文信息，这些信息是保证后续能够运行的必要参数</p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-python" data-language="python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">get_tool_runtime</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>        cls<span class="token punctuation">,</span>        provider_type<span class="token punctuation">:</span> ToolProviderType<span class="token punctuation">,</span>        provider_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        tool_name<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        tenant_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        invoke_from<span class="token punctuation">:</span> InvokeFrom <span class="token operator">=</span> InvokeFrom<span class="token punctuation">.</span>DEBUGGER<span class="token punctuation">,</span>        tool_invoke_from<span class="token punctuation">:</span> ToolInvokeFrom <span class="token operator">=</span> ToolInvokeFrom<span class="token punctuation">.</span>AGENT<span class="token punctuation">,</span>        credential_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    <span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token operator">></span> Union<span class="token punctuation">[</span>BuiltinTool<span class="token punctuation">,</span> PluginTool<span class="token punctuation">,</span> ApiTool<span class="token punctuation">,</span> WorkflowTool<span class="token punctuation">,</span> MCPTool<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><p>get_tool_runtime这个函数接受provider的类型和工具的名字，以此来确定到底要调用哪个provider</p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-python" data-language="python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">if</span> provider_type <span class="token operator">==</span> ToolProviderType<span class="token punctuation">.</span>BUILT_IN<span class="token punctuation">:</span>    <span class="token comment"># 获取 Provider</span>    provider_controller <span class="token operator">=</span> cls<span class="token punctuation">.</span>get_builtin_provider<span class="token punctuation">(</span>provider_id<span class="token punctuation">,</span> tenant_id<span class="token punctuation">)</span>    <span class="token comment"># 获取 Tool（无 runtime）</span>    builtin_tool <span class="token operator">=</span> provider_controller<span class="token punctuation">.</span>get_tool<span class="token punctuation">(</span>tool_name<span class="token punctuation">)</span>    <span class="token comment"># 查询数据库获取凭证配置</span>    builtin_provider <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>        db<span class="token punctuation">.</span>session<span class="token punctuation">.</span>query<span class="token punctuation">(</span>BuiltinToolProvider<span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token punctuation">.</span>where<span class="token punctuation">(</span>            BuiltinToolProvider<span class="token punctuation">.</span>tenant_id <span class="token operator">==</span> tenant_id<span class="token punctuation">,</span>            BuiltinToolProvider<span class="token punctuation">.</span>provider <span class="token operator">==</span> provider_id        <span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token punctuation">.</span>order_by<span class="token punctuation">(</span>BuiltinToolProvider<span class="token punctuation">.</span>is_default<span class="token punctuation">.</span>desc<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token punctuation">.</span>first<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>    <span class="token punctuation">)</span>    <span class="token comment"># ...中间的验证代码</span>    <span class="token comment"># 构建 ToolRuntime（核心！）</span>    runtime <span class="token operator">=</span> ToolRuntime<span class="token punctuation">(</span>        tenant_id<span class="token operator">=</span>tenant_id<span class="token punctuation">,</span>        credentials<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token builtin">dict</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>decrypted_credentials<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>           <span class="token comment"># 解密后的凭证</span>        credential_type<span class="token operator">=</span>CredentialType<span class="token punctuation">.</span>of<span class="token punctuation">(</span>builtin_provider<span class="token punctuation">.</span>credential_type<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        runtime_parameters<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>                              <span class="token comment"># 运行时参数</span>        invoke_from<span class="token operator">=</span>invoke_from<span class="token punctuation">,</span>        tool_invoke_from<span class="token operator">=</span>tool_invoke_from<span class="token punctuation">,</span>    <span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token comment"># 组装并返回（核心！）</span>    <span class="token keyword">return</span> builtin_tool<span class="token punctuation">.</span>fork_tool_runtime<span class="token punctuation">(</span>runtime<span class="token operator">=</span>runtime<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><p>我们获取到 provider 和 tools 之后，就构建 ToolRuntime，然后通过 fork 方法合并成新的 tool，最后就把这个交给 ToolEngine。</p><h3 id="关键能力验证"><a href="#关键能力验证" class="headerlink" title="关键能力验证"></a>关键能力验证</h3><table><thead><tr><th align="left">能力</th><th align="left">说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">Provider 决策</td><td align="left">动态决定服务提供商</td></tr><tr><td align="left">参数补充</td><td align="left">完善调用参数</td></tr><tr><td align="left">实例组装</td><td align="left">构建工具实例</td></tr></tbody></table><hr><h2 id="第二层：执行引擎层（ToolEngine）"><a href="#第二层：执行引擎层（ToolEngine）" class="headerlink" title="第二层：执行引擎层（ToolEngine）"></a>第二层：执行引擎层（ToolEngine）</h2><h3 id="引擎核心职责"><a href="#引擎核心职责" class="headerlink" title="引擎核心职责"></a>引擎核心职责</h3><p>ToolEngine 是具体执行层，负责工具的生命周期管理、前端通信、执行监控和数据持久化。</p><h3 id="执行流程详解"><a href="#执行流程详解" class="headerlink" title="执行流程详解"></a>执行流程详解</h3><h4 id="1-入口方法：agent-invoke（对话格式）"><a href="#1-入口方法：agent-invoke（对话格式）" class="headerlink" title="1. 入口方法：agent_invoke（对话格式）"></a>1. 入口方法：<code>agent_invoke</code>（对话格式）</h4><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-python" data-language="python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">agent_invoke</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>self<span class="token punctuation">,</span> tool_instance<span class="token punctuation">,</span> parameters<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>    <span class="token comment"># 1. 通知前端 - 执行开始</span>    self<span class="token punctuation">.</span>_notify_frontend<span class="token punctuation">(</span>status<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"started"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token comment"># 2. 进入实际执行逻辑</span>    result <span class="token operator">=</span> self<span class="token punctuation">.</span>_invoke<span class="token punctuation">(</span>tool_instance<span class="token punctuation">,</span> parameters<span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token comment"># 3. 后续处理...</span>    <span class="token keyword">return</span> result<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><p>如果是工作流： generic_invoke</p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-python" data-language="python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">generic_invoke</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>        tool<span class="token punctuation">:</span> Tool<span class="token punctuation">,</span>        tool_parameters<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">dict</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> Any<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        user_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        workflow_tool_callback<span class="token punctuation">:</span> DifyWorkflowCallbackHandler<span class="token punctuation">,</span>        workflow_call_depth<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">int</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        conversation_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        app_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        message_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    <span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token operator">></span> Generator<span class="token punctuation">[</span>ToolInvokeMessage<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>        <span class="token triple-quoted-string string">"""        Workflow invokes the tool with the given arguments.        """</span>        <span class="token keyword">try</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>            <span class="token comment"># hit the callback handler</span>            workflow_tool_callback<span class="token punctuation">.</span>on_tool_start<span class="token punctuation">(</span>tool_name<span class="token operator">=</span>tool<span class="token punctuation">.</span>entity<span class="token punctuation">.</span>identity<span class="token punctuation">.</span>name<span class="token punctuation">,</span> tool_inputs<span class="token operator">=</span>tool_parameters<span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token builtin">isinstance</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>tool<span class="token punctuation">,</span> WorkflowTool<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>  <span class="token comment">#控制深度，防止死循环</span>                tool<span class="token punctuation">.</span>workflow_call_depth <span class="token operator">=</span> workflow_call_depth <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token number">1</span>            <span class="token keyword">if</span> tool<span class="token punctuation">.</span>runtime <span class="token keyword">and</span> tool<span class="token punctuation">.</span>runtime<span class="token punctuation">.</span>runtime_parameters<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token comment"># 合并参数</span>                tool_parameters <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token operator">**</span>tool<span class="token punctuation">.</span>runtime<span class="token punctuation">.</span>runtime_parameters<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token operator">**</span>tool_parameters<span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>            response <span class="token operator">=</span> tool<span class="token punctuation">.</span>invoke<span class="token punctuation">(</span>                user_id<span class="token operator">=</span>user_id<span class="token punctuation">,</span>                tool_parameters<span class="token operator">=</span>tool_parameters<span class="token punctuation">,</span>                conversation_id<span class="token operator">=</span>conversation_id<span class="token punctuation">,</span>                app_id<span class="token operator">=</span>app_id<span class="token punctuation">,</span>                message_id<span class="token operator">=</span>message_id<span class="token punctuation">,</span>            <span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token comment"># hit the callback handler</span>            response <span class="token operator">=</span> workflow_tool_callback<span class="token punctuation">.</span>on_tool_execution<span class="token punctuation">(</span>                tool_name<span class="token operator">=</span>tool<span class="token punctuation">.</span>entity<span class="token punctuation">.</span>identity<span class="token punctuation">.</span>name<span class="token punctuation">,</span>                tool_inputs<span class="token operator">=</span>tool_parameters<span class="token punctuation">,</span>                tool_outputs<span class="token operator">=</span>response<span class="token punctuation">,</span>            <span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token keyword">return</span> response        <span class="token keyword">except</span> Exception <span class="token keyword">as</span> e<span class="token punctuation">:</span>            workflow_tool_callback<span class="token punctuation">.</span>on_tool_error<span class="token punctuation">(</span>e<span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token keyword">raise</span> e<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><p><strong>关键动作：</strong></p><ul><li>立即通知前端执行状态变更（开始执行）</li><li>委托 _invoke 进行实际工具调用</li><li>如果是工作流的话，会进行参数的合并</li></ul><h4 id="2-核心执行：-invoke-方法"><a href="#2-核心执行：-invoke-方法" class="headerlink" title="2. 核心执行：_invoke 方法"></a>2. 核心执行：_invoke 方法</h4><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-python" data-language="python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">_invoke</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>self<span class="token punctuation">,</span> tool<span class="token punctuation">,</span> parameters<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>    <span class="token comment"># 1. 记录执行开始时间</span>    start_time <span class="token operator">=</span> time<span class="token punctuation">.</span>time<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token keyword">try</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>        <span class="token comment"># 2. 调用 Tools.invoke 进入工具具体执行</span>        result <span class="token operator">=</span> tool<span class="token punctuation">.</span>invoke<span class="token punctuation">(</span>parameters<span class="token punctuation">)</span>                <span class="token comment"># 3. 计算执行耗时</span>        duration <span class="token operator">=</span> time<span class="token punctuation">.</span>time<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">-</span> start_time                <span class="token comment"># 4. 消息处理与数据持久化</span>        self<span class="token punctuation">.</span>_process_and_save<span class="token punctuation">(</span>result<span class="token punctuation">,</span> duration<span class="token punctuation">)</span>                <span class="token comment"># 5. 通知前端执行完成</span>        self<span class="token punctuation">.</span>_notify_frontend<span class="token punctuation">(</span>status<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"completed"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>                <span class="token keyword">return</span> result    <span class="token keyword">except</span> Exception <span class="token keyword">as</span> e<span class="token punctuation">:</span>        <span class="token comment"># 异常处理</span>        self<span class="token punctuation">.</span>_notify_frontend<span class="token punctuation">(</span>status<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"failed"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> error<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>e<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token keyword">raise</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><p>在这个逻辑里面，我们真正的开始调用tool去执行任务了，所以我们需要记录执行的耗时，同时向下传递，进入Tool的执行逻辑</p><h2 id="第三层：工具实现层（Tools）"><a href="#第三层：工具实现层（Tools）" class="headerlink" title="第三层：工具实现层（Tools）"></a>第三层：工具实现层（Tools）</h2><h3 id="工具核心职责"><a href="#工具核心职责" class="headerlink" title="工具核心职责"></a>工具核心职责</h3><p>Tools 层是具体业务逻辑层，负责参数处理、类型转换和实际业务执行。</p><h3 id="工具执行流程"><a href="#工具执行流程" class="headerlink" title="工具执行流程"></a>工具执行流程</h3><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="mermaid">sequenceDiagram    participant UI as 前端/回调    participant TE as ToolEngine    participant T as Tools (第三层)    participant DB as 数据库        TE->>UI: _notify_frontend(status="started")    TE->>TE: 记录 start_time        TE->>T: 调用 invoke(parameters)    activate T    T-->>TE: 返回执行结果 (result)    deactivate T        TE->>TE: 计算 duration (now - start_time)    TE->>DB: _process_and_save(result, duration)    TE->>UI: _notify_frontend(status="completed")    TE-->>UI: 返回最终结果</pre></div></figure><h3 id="详细步骤"><a href="#详细步骤" class="headerlink" title="详细步骤"></a>详细步骤</h3><table><thead><tr><th align="left">步骤</th><th align="left">方法</th><th align="left">职责</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">1</td><td align="left">Tools.invoke</td><td align="left">参数合并：将 Runtime 中的配置参数与用户传入参数融合</td></tr><tr><td align="left">2</td><td align="left">Tools.invoke</td><td align="left">类型转换：确保参数类型符合工具定义要求（如字符串转整数等）</td></tr><tr><td align="left">3</td><td align="left">子类._invoke</td><td align="left">业务执行：具体工具的实现逻辑（如调用外部 API、执行代码等）</td></tr><tr><td align="left">4</td><td align="left">Tools.invoke</td><td align="left">结果返回：将子类结果标准化后返回上层</td></tr></tbody></table><hr><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-python" data-language="python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">invoke</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>        self<span class="token punctuation">,</span>        user_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        tool_parameters<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">dict</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> Any<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        conversation_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        app_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        message_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    <span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token operator">></span> Generator<span class="token punctuation">[</span>ToolInvokeMessage<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span> self<span class="token punctuation">.</span>runtime <span class="token keyword">and</span> self<span class="token punctuation">.</span>runtime<span class="token punctuation">.</span>runtime_parameters<span class="token punctuation">:</span>            tool_parameters<span class="token punctuation">.</span>update<span class="token punctuation">(</span>self<span class="token punctuation">.</span>runtime<span class="token punctuation">.</span>runtime_parameters<span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token comment"># try parse tool parameters into the correct type</span>        tool_parameters <span class="token operator">=</span> self<span class="token punctuation">.</span>_transform_tool_parameters_type<span class="token punctuation">(</span>tool_parameters<span class="token punctuation">)</span>        result <span class="token operator">=</span> self<span class="token punctuation">.</span>_invoke<span class="token punctuation">(</span>            user_id<span class="token operator">=</span>user_id<span class="token punctuation">,</span>            tool_parameters<span class="token operator">=</span>tool_parameters<span class="token punctuation">,</span>            conversation_id<span class="token operator">=</span>conversation_id<span class="token punctuation">,</span>            app_id<span class="token operator">=</span>app_id<span class="token punctuation">,</span>            message_id<span class="token operator">=</span>message_id<span class="token punctuation">,</span>        <span class="token punctuation">)</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><p>invoke函数会检查是否有runtime参数，如果有，和tool_parameters合并，而且是tool_parameters优先，然后我们调用子类的具体实现方法：</p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-python" data-language="python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token decorator annotation punctuation">@abstractmethod</span><span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">_invoke</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>    self<span class="token punctuation">,</span>    user_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    tool_parameters<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">dict</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> Any<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    conversation_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    app_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    message_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token operator">></span> ToolInvokeMessage <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token builtin">list</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span>ToolInvokeMessage<span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> Generator<span class="token punctuation">[</span>ToolInvokeMessage<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>    <span class="token keyword">pass</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><p>抽象类，具体交给tool的子类执行</p><h2 id="总体流程"><a href="#总体流程" class="headerlink" title="总体流程"></a>总体流程</h2><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="mermaid">sequenceDiagram    participant TE as ToolEngine (上层)    participant T as Tools 基类    participant ST as Tools 子类 (具体实现)    participant EXT as 外部服务/API        TE->>T: invoke(user_id, parameters)        alt 参数检查        T->>T: 检查并合并 Runtime 参数        T->>T: 执行 _transform_tool_parameters_type        Note right of T: 类型转换(如 String -> Int)    end        T->>ST: 调用 _invoke (抽象方法实现)    activate ST    ST->>EXT: 发起实际业务请求    EXT-->>ST: 返回原始数据    ST-->>T: 返回 ToolInvokeMessage    deactivate ST        T-->>TE: 返回标准化结果</pre></div></figure><hr><h2 id="架构设计亮点"><a href="#架构设计亮点" class="headerlink" title="架构设计亮点"></a>架构设计亮点</h2><h3 id="1-职责分离（Separation-of-Concerns）"><a href="#1-职责分离（Separation-of-Concerns）" class="headerlink" title="1. 职责分离（Separation of Concerns）"></a>1. 职责分离（Separation of Concerns）</h3><ul><li><strong>ToolManage</strong>：专注决策与组装，无执行逻辑</li><li><strong>ToolEngine</strong>：专注生命周期与基础设施，无业务逻辑</li><li><strong>Tools</strong>：专注业务实现，无调度逻辑</li></ul><h3 id="2-可观测性（Observability）"><a href="#2-可观测性（Observability）" class="headerlink" title="2. 可观测性（Observability）"></a>2. 可观测性（Observability）</h3><ul><li><strong>前端实时通知</strong>：执行开始&#x2F;结束状态同步</li><li><strong>性能指标</strong>：执行时间记录</li><li><strong>数据持久化</strong>：执行结果自动存档</li></ul><h3 id="3-扩展性（Extensibility）"><a href="#3-扩展性（Extensibility）" class="headerlink" title="3. 扩展性（Extensibility）"></a>3. 扩展性（Extensibility）</h3><ul><li><strong>新工具接入</strong>：只需实现 子类._invoke</li><li><strong>新 Provider 支持</strong>：ToolManage 动态决策</li><li><strong>参数处理</strong>：统一的类型转换机制</li></ul><h3 id="4-容错设计"><a href="#4-容错设计" class="headerlink" title="4. 容错设计"></a>4. 容错设计</h3><ul><li><strong>分层异常捕获</strong>：每层可独立处理异常</li><li><strong>数据持久化</strong>：即使前端断开，执行记录依然保存</li><li><strong>超时控制</strong>：Engine 层可监控执行时长</li></ul><hr><h2 id="典型调用时序"><a href="#典型调用时序" class="headerlink" title="典型调用时序"></a>典型调用时序</h2><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="mermaid">sequenceDiagram    participant 前端    participant ToolManage    participant ToolEngine    participant Tools    participant 外部服务    participant 数据库    前端->>ToolManage: 调用工具    ToolManage->>ToolEngine: 决策/组装    ToolEngine->>前端: 开始通知    Note right of 前端: 前端展示    ToolEngine->>Tools: 调用    Tools->>Tools: 参数处理    Tools->>外部服务: 调用    activate 外部服务    Note right of 外部服务: 执行    外部服务-->>Tools: 返回    deactivate 外部服务    Tools->>Tools: 结果处理    Tools-->>ToolEngine: 返回    ToolEngine->>数据库: 持久化    ToolEngine->>前端: 结束通知    Note right of 前端: 前端更新    ToolEngine-->>前端: 返回结果</pre></div></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
